Newest son-in-law<br/><br/>A very successful businessman had a meeting with his new son-in-law. &quot;I love my daughter, and now I welcome you into the family,&quot; said the man. &quot;To show you how much we care for you, I'm making you a 50-50 partner in my business. All you have to do is go to the factory every day and learn the operations.&quot; 
<br /><br />The son-in-law interrupted, &quot;I hate factories. I can't stand the noise.&quot; 
<br /><br />&quot;I see,&quot; replied the father-in-law. &quot;Well, then you'll work in the office and take charge of some of the operations.&quot; 
<br /><br />&quot;I hate office work,&quot; said the son-on-law. &quot;I can't stand being stuck behind a desk all day.&quot; 
<br /><br />&quot;Wait a minute,&quot; said the father-in-law. &quot;I just make you half-owner of a moneymaking organization, but you don't like factories and won't work in a office. What am I going to do with you?&quot; 
